name: inner_join
constraint: (declare-const CO_SPEC Int)(declare-const RO_SPEC Int)(declare-const CI_SPEC Int)(declare-const CI2_SPEC Int)(declare-const RI_SPEC Int)(declare-const RI2_SPEC Int)(assert (or (and (<= RO_SPEC RI_SPEC) (>= RO_SPEC RI2_SPEC)) (and (>= RO_SPEC RI_SPEC) (<= RO_SPEC RI2_SPEC))))(assert (<= CO_SPEC (- (+ CI_SPEC CI2_SPEC) 1)))
(declare-const IH_SPEC Int)(declare-const OH_SPEC Int)(declare-const IH2_SPEC Int)(declare-const OH2_SPEC Int)(assert (>= (+ IH_SPEC IH2_SPEC) OH_SPEC))
(declare-const IC_SPEC Int)(declare-const IC2_SPEC Int)(declare-const OC_SPEC Int)(assert (>= (+ IC_SPEC IC2_SPEC) OC_SPEC))
